{"article_id":"EC2EX4nmRQeLm7T0","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Donald Trump directed Michael Cohen to arrange hush-money payments with two women","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"because then-candidate Trump \" was very concerned about how this would affect the election \"","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"if their allegations of affairs became public ,","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"the president ' s former personal attorney said in an exclusive interview with .","depth":2},{"id":4,"text":"Interested in Donald Trump ?","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"Add Donald Trump as an interest","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"to stay up to date on the latest Donald Trump news , video , and analysis from .","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"Add Interest","depth":3},{"id":8,"text":"Cohen ' s comments are his first","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"since being sentenced earlier this week to three years in federal prison for financial crimes , lying to Congress and two campaign finance violations in connection with the deals with the women ,","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"Karen McDougal and Stormy Daniels ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"who claim past affairs with Trump .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"\" I knew","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"what I was doing was wrong , \"","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"Cohen told ' Chief Anchor George Stephanopoulos .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"\" I stood up before the world","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"[ Wednesday ]","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"and I accepted the responsibility for my actions . \"","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"When asked if the president also knew","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"it was wrong to make the payments ,","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"Cohen replied ,","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"\" Of course , \"","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"adding","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"that the purpose was to \" help [ Trump ] and his campaign . \"","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"Cohen said","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"he is \" angry at himself \" for his role in the deals ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"but that he did it out of \" blind loyalty \" to Trump .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"\" I gave loyalty to someone","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"who , truthfully , does not deserve loyalty , \"","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"Federal prosecutors in the Southern District of New York have implicated , but not charged , the president in the deals","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"reached in the closing weeks of the 2016 election .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"They allege","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"that Cohen acted \" in coordination with and at the direction of \" Trump ,","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"according to court filings .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"Prosecutors also reached a non-prosecution agreement with AMI , the publishers of the National Inquirer ,","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"in which the tabloid admitted to making a $ 150,000 payment to McDougal \" in concert \" with the Trump campaign .","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"The president has denied allegations of the affairs","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"-- but has had shifting explanations","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"about when he learned about the payments to the women .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"He has also contended","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"that the deals were private and unrelated to the campaign","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"and that","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"if anything illegal occurred ,","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"it was Cohen ' s responsibility .","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"Trump has lashed out at Cohen since his sentencing ,","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"contending in a Thursday tweet","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"that his former close confidant only agreed to plead guilty","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"\" in order to embarrass the president","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"and get a much reduced prison sentence ,","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"which he did . \"","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"\" It is absolutely not true , \"","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"Cohen said .","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"\" Under no circumstances do I want to embarrass the president .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"He knows the truth .","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"I know the truth . \"","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"Cohen was particularly distressed by another Trump tweet on Thursday ,","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"in which the president implied","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"that prosecutors","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"investigating Cohen","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"had let his wife and father-in-law off the hook .","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"\" Instead of him taking responsibility for his actions ,","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"what does he do ? \"","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"Cohen said .","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"\" He attacks my family . \"","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"And Cohen refuted the president ' s contention","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"that he never directed Cohen to do anything wrong .","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"\" I do n't think","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"there is anybody","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"that believes that , \"","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"Cohen told Stephanopoulos .","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"\" First of all , nothing at the Trump organization was ever done","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"unless it was run through Mr. Trump .","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"He directed me to make the payments ,","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"he directed me to become involved in these matters .","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"\" He knows the truth .","depth":14},{"id":76,"text":"I know the truth .","depth":14},{"id":77,"text":"Others know the truth , \"","depth":14},{"id":78,"text":"Cohen continued .","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"\" And here is the truth :","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"People of the United States of America , people of the world , do n't believe what he is saying .","depth":15},{"id":81,"text":"The man does n't tell the truth .","depth":15},{"id":82,"text":"And it is sad that I should take responsibility for his dirty deeds . \"","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"When confronted about his convictions","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"for lying to Congress","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"and for tax evasion and banking crimes ,","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"Cohen said","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"he was \" done with the lying .","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"I am done being loyal to President Trump","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"and my first loyalty belongs to my wife , my daughter , my son and this country . \"","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"\" Because the special counsel stated emphatically","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"that the information","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"that I gave to them","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"is credible and helpful , \"","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"Cohen replied .","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"\" There ' s a substantial amount of information","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"that they possessed","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"that corroborates the fact","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"that I am telling the truth . \"","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"Cohen","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"--","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"who is due to report to prison on March 6 --","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"has professed his willingness","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"to continue to answer questions for special counsel Robert Mueller and other federal and state investigators .","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"He declined in the interview to answer specific questions about the Mueller investigation \" out of respect for process . \"","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"\" I don ' t want to jeopardize any of their investigations , \"","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"But","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"when asked","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"if he thinks","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"the president is telling the truth about the Russia probe ,","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"Cohen replied simply ,","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"\" No . \"","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"Cohen once said","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"he would \" take a bullet \" for the president ,","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"but now he finds himself opposing the president","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"and facing the prospect","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"of becoming a witness against him .","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"\" It ' s never good to be on the wrong side of the president of the United States of America ,","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"but somehow or another this task has now fallen onto my shoulders","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"and","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"as I also stated ...","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"I will spend the rest of my life","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"in order to fix the mistake","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"that I made . \"","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"Cohen said","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"as he observes Trump ' s actions in the White House ,","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"he barely recognizes the man","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"he served for more than a decade at the Trump organization .","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"\" He ' s a very different individual , \"","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"Cohen said .","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"\" I think","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"the pressure of the job is much more","depth":13},{"id":133,"text":"than what he thought","depth":14},{"id":134,"text":"it was going to be .","depth":14},{"id":135,"text":"It ' s not like the Trump organization","depth":13},{"id":136,"text":"where he would bark out orders","depth":14},{"id":137,"text":"and people would blindly follow what he wanted done .","depth":14},{"id":138,"text":"There ' s a system here ;","depth":15},{"id":139,"text":"he doesn ' t understand the system","depth":15},{"id":140,"text":"and it ' s sad","depth":15},{"id":141,"text":"because the country has never been more divisive","depth":15},{"id":142,"text":"and one of the hopes","depth":16},{"id":143,"text":"that I have","depth":16},{"id":144,"text":"out of the punishment","depth":17},{"id":145,"text":"that I ' ve received","depth":17},{"id":146,"text":"as well as the cooperation","depth":17},{"id":147,"text":"that I have given","depth":17},{"id":148,"text":"I will be remembered in history as helping to bring this country back together .","depth":14},{"id":149,"text":"\" I will not be the villain of his story , \"","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"he said .","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":301,"left":154,"right":300,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":153,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":0,"right":152,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":300,"left":157,"right":299,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":157,"left":156,"right":7,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":156,"left":4,"right":155,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":155,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":299,"left":178,"right":298,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":178,"left":160,"right":177,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":8,"right":159,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":9,"right":158,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":177,"left":171,"right":176,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":171,"left":165,"right":170,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":165,"left":162,"right":164,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":162,"left":161,"right":14,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":161,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":164,"left":163,"right":17,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":163,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":17